{
  "stem": "18186.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 21.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was '45 for real, and we were married in '46.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Germany-- still in Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in Hanover.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First off, we had everything-- the UNRRA gave us-- supported us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got support from the UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we really didn't have anything to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we had a good time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to movies.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to-- and then I get-- got pregnant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I have my son.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was busy with my son.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was like normal life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we kept on talking from all those years, what we went through for the-- you know, we left the family, and we lost everybody.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I'm alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And not too many people are left-- were left all alone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There are families that had-- like my husband, for instance, he survived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "His-- his three sisters survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He only lost his father from starvation in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And his mother went in the oven with his niece, little niece, and his brother was also-- his younger brother didn't survive, which he'll show you.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But then more and more people survived, find family, a sister, a brother, and some nobody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I survived with nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there was a committee-- a committee, Jewish committee.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we registered before going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then came-- now then it came-- the soldiers came in to see-- Jewish soldiers, British.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They sort of come into our place, and they would-- wanted to know how we survived and what.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they asked us--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we asked him-- well, there was-- maybe was one guy special that he was questioning a lot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he was Jewish himself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he wanted to help us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said to us, do you have any relatives in United States or in Britain, or so?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or in Israel?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
